name: AntsyPantry
description:
AntsyPantry was made for the Trijam 172 in 2 hours and 59 minutes. 

Click and drag the food to balance the shelf in the pantry!

Credits for art and sound:

tilemap by Pixel Frog- https://pixelfrog-assets.itch.io/pirate-bomb

food sprites by VectorPixelStar - https://vectorpixelstar.itch.io/food

food sounds by SeanPal - https://seanpal.itch.io/fruit-falling-sfx-pack-1

music by SVL -  https://svl.itch.io/rpg-music-pack-svl
